{"word":"G565 - ἀπέρχομαι - apérchomai - ap-erkh'-om-ahee - Come","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀπέρχομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">apérchomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ap-erkh'-om-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Come</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - போ, ஏறு, சேர், தொடர்ந்து"},{"paragraph":"to go away (from a place), to depart"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G575 - ἀπό - apó - apo'/575\">G575</a> and <a href=\"#/G2064 - ἔρχομαι - érchomai - er'-khom-ahee/2064\">G2064</a>; to <i>go off</i> (that is, <i>depart</i>), <i>aside</i> (that is, <i>apart</i>) or <i>behind</i> (that is, <i>follow</i>), literally or figuratively: - come, depart, go (aside, away, back, out, . . . ways), pass away, be past.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1330/1330\">G1330</a>, <a href=\"#/G1525/1525\">G1525</a>, <a href=\"#/G1831/1831\">G1831</a>, <a href=\"#/G1904/1904\">G1904</a>, <a href=\"#/G2064/2064\">G2064</a>, <a href=\"#/G3922/3922\">G3922</a>, <a href=\"#/G3928/3928\">G3928</a>, <a href=\"#/G4022/4022\">G4022</a>, <a href=\"#/G4281/4281\">G4281</a>, <a href=\"#/G4334/4334\">G4334</a>, <a href=\"#/G4905/4905\">G4905</a>, <a href=\"#/G565/565\">G565</a>"}]}